God gave us Eden.

44:11.655 --> 44:13.534
He gave us perfection.

44:15.335 --> 44:17.094
And what did we do with it?

44:18.735 --> 44:20.454
We destroyed it.

44:21.775 --> 44:23.135
We sinned.

44:24.454 --> 44:28.934
And we grew prideful
and vengeful and angry.

44:30.295 --> 44:34.494
