44:41.255 --> 44:42.974
How dare we?

44:43.014 --> 44:44.855
It is us.

44:45.894 --> 44:48.014
It is our doing.

44:49.375 --> 44:51.695
And it is all we deserve.

44:51.735 --> 44:56.934
God will always forgive,
he will always offer salvation.

44:56.974 --> 44:59.414
But I don't believe all of us
deserve it.

45:01.735 --> 45:06.014
If we sin, we break God's law.

45:06.054 --> 45:10.815
If you sin,
you do not deserve his love.

45:10.855 --> 45:13.775
You do not deserve his salvation.

